{
  "title": "Softly Sweet Syrian Bulgur Pilaf",
  "description": "A malty, chewy, and romantic Syrian dish featuring freshly chopped parsley, shio-cure, and lacto-vegetarian friendly ingredients, perfect for a special occasion.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
  "diet": [
